To install this simple image gallery, follow these steps:

    * Copy the module folder to your kohana modules directory, and name it 'sigal'
    * Add MODPATH.'sigal' to your module list in config.php
    * Copy config/sigal.php to your application folder, and configure it for your environment
    * Copy the contents of the media folder to where you defined the media-folder in the config.
    * Chmod 777 the upload folder, defined in your config.

OPTIONAL
    * Ensure that you have no routes that would block /album, /photo, /admin/album and /admin/photo
	* Have fun!

